    "Finally, \"Conclusions\" claims the increasing relevance of emerging economies in AE due to its growing capabilities in the area.",
    "Additionally, improving cultural and geographical representativeness of AE contributes to foster the diffusion and acceptance of AI in health-related R&D worldwide.",
    "Reconfigurations of biomedical knowledge infrastructuresFor decades, computation, AI, machine learning (ML) tools and other digital technologies have contributed to a technical, epistemic, and geographic shift of biomedical knowledge infrastructures internationally.",
